==行車路線==
'''海濱花園開'''經：[[怡樂街_(荃灣)|怡樂街]]、[[永順街|永順街]]、[[馬頭壩道|馬頭壩道]]、[[聯仁街|聯仁街]]、[[沙咀道|沙咀道]]、[[大河道|大河道]]及[[西樓角路|西樓角路]]。

'''荃灣站開'''經：西樓角路、大河道、[[楊屋道|楊屋道]]、馬頭壩道、永順街及怡樂街<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ushb.net/rtinfo/KMB/KMB238m.php |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-08-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070813081738/http://www.ushb.net/rtinfo/KMB/KMB238M.php |archivedate=2007-08-13 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.i-busnet.com/busroute/kmb/kmbr238m.php |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-08-14 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201081234/http://www.i-busnet.com/busroute/kmb/kmbr238m.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.stopreporter.com/index.php?click=kmbsearch.php&route=238m&company=kmb |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-08-14 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305000501/http://www.stopreporter.com/index.php?click=kmbsearch.php&route=238m&company=kmb |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

